<br>
Let me put it this way, the Bard instant DD, the bonus &quot;damage&quot; is based 90% upon your acuity stat, versus your spec level.  Getting Music from 44 to 60 (+16) meant a difference of 5-10 damage against a yellow con target.<br>
<br>
Also CDW has never altered your base damage rate (like Left Axe does), it should only alter your CDW style damage and your offhand swing chance.  I haven't heard anything yet on the benefits exceeding 50 spec (nor seen any from my personal test), and how that affects your offhand swing rate, or if Duelist Reflexes allows you to hover or exceed 50 spec &quot;cap&quot;.<br>
